                            <comment id="13537782" author="jonas" created="Fri, 21 Dec 2012 10:04:58 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Or even more simple&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;private boolean shouldTrigger()&lt;br/&gt;
{&lt;br/&gt;
return isStopped() == false &amp;amp;&amp;amp;&lt;br/&gt;
isEnabled(getComponent()) &amp;amp;&amp;amp;&lt;br/&gt;
getComponent().findPage() != null;&lt;br/&gt;
}&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Unless, of course, there&apos;s a particular reason why a WEBpage parent is needed and some other Page wouldn&apos;t be ok as well...&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
